---
import Handbook from "../layouts/Handbook.astro";
---
<Handbook title="Map & Transportation" current="more">
  <h1>Map & Transportation</h1>
  <section class="panel">
    <h2>必裝 App</h2>
    <ul class="list">
      <li><a href="https://map.naver.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Naver Map</a> — 路線與出口</li>
      <li><a href="https://map.kakao.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Kakao Map</a> — 備援導航</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.t-money.co.kr" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">T-money</a> — 交通卡資訊</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.letskorail.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Korail</a> — KTX</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section class="panel">
    <h2>本趟原則</h2>
    <p>不租車 · 每天最多 1–2 個相鄰區域 · 腳痠就改計程車 · 移動日不塞景點</p>
    <p class="muted">詳見 handbook/city-transport.md</p>
  </section>
</Handbook>
